        <h2 class="centered-title">FOREX ONE SYSTEM</h2>
        <div class="hero-image"></div>
        <div class="product-grid">
            <div class="product">
                <h3>Summary</h3>
                <p>The "Forex One System" is a trading strategy designed for use on the Metatrader 4 platform, particularly for the EUR/USD currency pair on a 1-hour chart. It provides a set of rules for generating buy and sell signals based on specific indicators and templates.</p>

                <h3>Key Components and Setup</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Metatrader 4 Platform: A free trading software needed to run the system.</li>
                    <li>System Files: Download and unzip the Forex One System file to obtain the necessary indicators and templates.</li>
                    <li>Installation:
                        <ul>
                            <li>Copy the `.ex4` files (indicators) to the `C:\ProgramFiles\MetaTrader4\experts\indicators` directory.</li>
                            <li>Copy the `.tpl` file (template) to the `C:\ProgramFiles\MetaTrader4\templates` directory.</li>
                            <li>Restart Metatrader, open a 1-hour chart for EUR/USD, right-click on the chart, and apply the Forex One System template.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Buy and Sell Rules</h3>
                <h4>Sell Signal</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Red Moon: Indicates a possible sell.</li>
                    <li>Red Bar: Confirms the sell signal.</li>
                    <li>Enter Sell: Execute a sell order.</li>
                    <li>Stop Loss (SL): Set at 40 pips from the entry point.</li>
                    <li>Take Profit (TP):
                        <ul>
                            <li>TP1: 40 pips from entry, then move the stop to the entry.</li>
                            <li>TP2: 80 pips, then move the stop 50 pips.</li>
                            <li>TP3: 120 pips, then move the stop 50 pips.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <h4>Buy Signal</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Blue Moon: Indicates a possible buy.</li>
                    <li>Blue Bar: Confirms the buy signal.</li>
                    <li>Enter Buy: Execute a buy order.</li>
                    <li>Stop Loss (SL): Set at 40 pips from the entry point.</li>
                    <li>Take Profit (TP):
                        <ul>
                            <li>TP1: 40 pips from entry, then move the stop to the entry.</li>
                            <li>TP2: 80 pips, then move the stop 50 pips.</li>
                            <li>TP3: 120 pips, then move the stop 50 pips.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Additional Notes</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Best Currency: EUR/USD.</li>
                    <li>Best Timeframe: 1-hour chart (H1).</li>
                    <li>Testing Period: It's recommended to test the strategy on a demo account for at least 40 days to understand its mechanics and market conditions before using it on a real account.</li>
                </ul>

